### Health check
GET http://localhost:13000/health

### Register (creates a user)
POST http://localhost:13000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Login (returns JWT)
POST http://localhost:13000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### (Optional) Paste your token here after login:
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_LOGIN

### List schools (public)
GET http://localhost:13000/schools

### Create school (protected)
POST http://localhost:13000/schools
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Toronto Tech Institute",
  "city": "Toronto"
}

### Get school by id (public)
# Replace 1 with a real id from the list/create response
GET http://localhost:13000/schools/1

### Update school (protected)
# Replace 1 with a real id
PUT http://localhost:13000/schools/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Toronto Tech Institute (Updated)",
  "city": "Toronto"
}

### Delete school (protected)
# Replace 1 with a real id
DELETE http://localhost:13000/schools/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
